CompanyDescription.value: IO Biotech Inc is a clinical-stage biopharmaceutical company developing novel, immune-modulating cancer therapies based on T-win technology platform. The product candidates are designed to induce the immune system to simultaneously target and disrupt multiple pathways that regulate tumor-induced immunosuppression.
